### ðŸ“Š Aggregate Functions

Aggregate functions do math on table data.

Example table: **groceries** (id, name, quantity)

---

### ðŸ§® Examples

```sql
SELECT SUM(quantity) FROM groceries;   -- adds all quantities (total)
SELECT MAX(quantity) FROM groceries;   -- finds the largest value
SELECT MIN(quantity) FROM groceries;   -- finds the smallest value
```

